snippet.title: Turnabout of the Final Day [FT] Grief, and learning to Heal
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty First-Time Playthrough]

WARNING: THIS CASE CONTAINS JUMPSCARES AND PRETTY UNSETTLING MOMENTS
This case also touches on certain topics of mental health.. that could make people quite uncomfortable, like isolation and trauma.

I was promised horror and I certainly got horror, but gosh, this feels like a very real depiction of reacting to trauma and loss, the feelings that take hold after, the fears, the regrets, and the struggle to pick yourself back up and keep going...
-----------------------------------------
Turnabout of the Final Day, by Super Legenda!

This case also happens after the events of Dual Destinies, and containts heavy spoilers of it.

The Final Day is coming.

Losing someone... dear to you, will always make our life hell for a long time. The pain can heal, new memories can be crafted, but scars, remains.

This is a story about how Athena Cykes, the young attorney, started to lose Everything, and how she deals with it... Or tries to.

Made for the Shelter in Place competition...

Find it on AA Online here: http://www.aaonline.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?t=12836&hilit=final+day
